I can confirm that after installing Comodo Firewall, I am seeing the crashes in Google Chrome.<br><br>I think the crashes seem to go away after blocking the COMODO Guard32 DLL in this way:<br><br>Sandbox Settings &gt; Resource Access &gt; File Access &gt; Blocked Access<br>Click Edit/Add, and paste:<br><strong>*\Guard32.dll</strong><br><br>Would like to know if applying this setting fixes the problem also for you.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3">tzuk</a> — Thu Aug 01, 2013 6:23 am</p><hr />
